為常<br />\n-到法庭比假口供"},{"pid":"d159345044fff56694567790ac3b8667a8332a1d","tid":1505417,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"[破局方向]國際文宣戰，但需要全香港人幫手做一件小事 long but must read<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504158</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n929全球集會賀國慶"},{"pid":"1cff96d1994b4350da09be7e4cf3d29027633e43","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3db5fb66d44bd0a4262ea6c86ee8501321dbada","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6ce540b694e453d98558192aadcfc2b46d4fd5d","tid":1505417,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"解散警隊，刻不容緩！"},{"pid":"f6d04d28381faebec61e67ef768026bfe9a0b7fe","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea5b488f16e85b86e13938b2b64867a74f839612","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9851512e42ed3f17c67eb498ffeb88bba9956df4","tid":1505417,"uid":303141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"acc848b13e084ba7c74208da9e67abb4386fabe3","tid":1505417,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"其實呢十年，公務員退休潮，出現咗大量空缺，導致青黃不接，警隊質素每況愈下<br />\n警隊唯有不斷聘人手去填補呢啲空缺，你短時間內填補大量人手，警隊好難去有揀岩人，加上退休潮造成左大量嘅晉升機會，佢哋為咗升職會搏表現，控制示威場面上佢哋會積極聽命上頭嘅指令，而呢啲上頭都係啱啱升職無奈嘅督察或者係警司，成個警隊已經腐敗不堪"},{"pid":"fb2af6bd5b5927abe70bc7c13da37221c6df8886","tid":1505417,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"你見呢幾年無論係總督察或者係警司佢哋都好後生，呢啲現象都係公務員退休潮造成嘅結果，都係令警隊淪落到今日嘅田地嘅結果"},{"pid":"3da8ae88c23b8da4ece7b67b1a8c2e4fcee0be8b","tid":1505417,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"班仆街做到咁高職位唔係因為佢哋嘅能力，而係短時間內出現大量嘅空缺，警隊填補呢啲空缺，唯有去短時間內晉升大量未必符合條件嘅人"},{"pid":"e579b70ae67e6610558b9118c7c4e573a4544735","tid":1505417,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"本人會<del>竭誠依法</del>為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，<br />\n<br />\n<del>遵從支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，<br />\n<br />\n</del>以<del>不</del>畏懼、<del>不</del>徇私、<del>不</del>對他人懷惡意、<br />\n<del>不</del>敵視他人<del>及忠誠努力</del>的態度行使職權，執行職務，<br />\n<br />\n並且亳不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切<del>合法</del>命令。"},{"pid":"8b5bf772689c548005a9fc7f04e124489d2485ea","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91006c9b9d5ba28eeeb0c806e005a303310d324b","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13609c3fa696b5fb74472dfc0f30619e5a7f5319","tid":1505417,"uid":167758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"bb4323993f45c610d338871dfbf0a0e13ed34a40","tid":1505417,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"解散警隊!!!!"},{"pid":"accee1f27ab13eb946125e3d66756b93f9c1bd6c","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"991f8ad7a3a7e6168f6b00e672a38d612aa3f88d","tid":1505417,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"203968de5bafa61a690ca339e145ed3e3bedfe56","tid":1505417,"uid":296194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"清算警察"},{"pid":"977be2decf38bb7b09dd2ac05a49d9e897cfa893","tid":1505417,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c62486b0f2f3dffd92d87b378553e7374272a24","tid":1505417,"u